1
00:00:58,085 --> 00:01:01,061
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:01,061 --> 00:01:03,031
=Episode 11=

3
00:01:03,031 --> 00:01:07,053
(Surrounded by a Pack of Wolves)

4
00:01:08,040 --> 00:01:09,959
I brought Zhaoxi back.

5
00:01:10,700 --> 00:01:13,920
He's been traveling and staying with me.

6
00:01:15,599 --> 00:01:18,560
How could I fail to tell
if he's my husband?

7
00:01:19,439 --> 00:01:20,239
Master Wenshuang.

8
00:01:20,959 --> 00:01:24,799
There has never been romance between us.

9
00:01:25,599 --> 00:01:27,000
I am your sister-in-law now.

10
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:29,120
It will remain this way forever.

11
00:02:49,879 --> 00:02:50,960
What took you so long?

12
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:54,800
Zhaoxi just came back from the yamen.

13
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:58,520
Who'd thought we'd received such news?

14
00:02:59,599 --> 00:03:02,960
The authorities retrieved these
from the bandits.

15
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:07,039
The bandits confessed
that they killed Zhaoxi,

16
00:03:07,319 --> 00:03:10,199
and threw him into the wolf pit,
where hungry wolves devoured him.

17
00:03:11,879 --> 00:03:14,120
His remains are still at the yamen.

18
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:18,520
They hope we can
claim the body early tomorrow.

19
00:03:19,479 --> 00:03:20,280
But

20
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:23,879
if that's the case,

21
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,280
who is that man you brought back?

22
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:33,159
- Chaosheng...
- What are you implying?

23
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:37,319
Zhaoxi is back home safe.
Shouldn't we be grateful?

24
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:41,759
Or perhaps, you don't want him back?

25
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:45,840
Master Zhaoxi is back safe and sound.

26
00:03:46,319 --> 00:03:50,120
Shouldn't the authorities
try to identify the deceased?

27
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:52,759
Zhaoxi is back.

28
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:58,039
Why are you so sure that's him
when the body hasn't been identified?

29
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,360
It seems as though...

30
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:04,400
(you were at the crime scene that day.)

31
00:04:33,519 --> 00:04:36,120
It's so late. Why are you all here?

32
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:50,720
The night is chilly,
so I brought you a cloak

33
00:04:50,959 --> 00:04:52,800
just in case you get cold.

34
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,920
This is Master Zhaoxi?

35
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:59,480
Let's find out if he's an imposter.

36
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:11,879
It's not a disguise.

37
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,839
Wenshuang, what are you doing?

38
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:18,399
Sorry, I didn't mean it.

39
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:23,279
Alright, I'll take his belongings back.

40
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:57,000
Why did you come with Xuanji?

41
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,439
I met her outside the front hall.

42
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:03,519
She was eavesdropping
on your conversation.

43
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:06,920
Zhaoxi just came back from the yamen.

44
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:10,519
Who'd thought we'd received such news?

45
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:26,800
Is that really Gu Zhaoxi's body
in the yamen?

46
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,279
I don't know.

47
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:38,480
Let's think about what to do later then.

48
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,920
Sorry, let me apply medicine for you.

49
00:06:59,279 --> 00:07:01,160
Thank you, dear.

50
00:07:12,576 --> 00:07:15,520
(Fufeng Pavilion)

51
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:35,040
(But I'm frail and chronically ill.)

52
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,279
(If you are reluctant,)

53
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:42,519
(I'll tell my father
to cancel the marriage.)

54
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,600
(Master Zhaoxi,)

55
00:07:51,399 --> 00:07:52,279
(I'm willing.)

56
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:59,480
In that case,
I will wait for your return.

57
00:08:33,519 --> 00:08:34,320
Young Madam.

58
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:35,480
What's wrong?

59
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:37,720
Master Zhaoxi hasn't returned.

60
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:40,759
We found his carriage and bloodstains
on his way back to the city.

61
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:43,200
Master Zhaoxi is missing.

62
00:09:01,279 --> 00:09:01,840
Master.

63
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,440
Master Zhaoxi is...

64
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:17,399
I didn't expect the family head
to let you tag along.

65
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,799
But fortunately, you were there.

66
00:09:25,279 --> 00:09:26,480
Heaven mission.

67
00:09:26,679 --> 00:09:27,639
Well,

68
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:31,480
are those people in black
General Shen's enemies

69
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:32,919
or mine?

70
00:09:33,759 --> 00:09:37,200
- Master.
- I can't believe the Heaven mission

71
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,720
was leaked.

72
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,200
I pledge my loyalty to you.

73
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:46,320
I will never betray you.

74
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:53,279
I know that if there's anyone
I can trust in this world,

75
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,240
that would be you.

76
00:09:58,480 --> 00:10:00,600
You saved my life.

77
00:10:01,039 --> 00:10:03,919
Even if the whole Xuanji Pavilion
turns against you one day,

78
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:07,559
I will fight a bloody path for you
with my life.

79
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,399
Get up.

80
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:15,960
Don't

81
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:17,840
talk like that.

82
00:10:18,879 --> 00:10:20,480
People might hear you.

83
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,120
But remember,

84
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:25,759
if I find out that you've lied to me,

85
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:30,679
I will not let you off easily.

86
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:37,960
You haven't done something, right?

87
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:45,919
Before the mission,
Master Zhaoxi asked me

88
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:49,519
whether there was
something you liked or held dear.

89
00:10:49,919 --> 00:10:53,279
I said that you once
wore a bead bracelet

90
00:10:53,679 --> 00:10:56,080
and suddenly stopped wearing it
for some reason.

91
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:57,679
It might have been lost.

92
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,759
He said, "Alright."

93
00:11:00,759 --> 00:11:04,159
And he wanted you to meet him
at Fufeng Pavilion after the mission.

94
00:11:05,399 --> 00:11:07,679
The death guards
have no fixed residence.

95
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:10,000
Although you're not married yet,

96
00:11:10,559 --> 00:11:13,200
he's already left a courtyard for you
at Fufeng Pavilion.

97
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:16,279
He said that you're welcome to stay
whenever you want

98
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:21,200
and that the Fufeng Pavilion
will be your home.

99
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:28,559
(But Master Zhaoxi also said)

100
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:31,799
(that marriage
is a lifelong commitment.)

101
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:34,159
(If you ever change your mind,)

102
00:11:34,639 --> 00:11:37,000
(your marriage
can be called off at any time.)

103
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:43,120
I'll retrieve the corpse
from the yamen tomorrow morning.

104
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:44,399
No.

105
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:47,039
Send someone to guard it.

106
00:11:48,519 --> 00:11:51,000
If someone
wants to identify the corpse...

107
00:11:53,799 --> 00:11:54,299
Understood.

108
00:11:54,919 --> 00:11:55,919
One more thing.

109
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:04,440
Weren't you certain that he was dead?

110
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,360
I saw it with my own eyes.

111
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:09,600
Xuanji Pavilion
specializes in the art of disguise.

112
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:12,279
They must have used some unknown method.

113
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:14,120
Are you that sure?

114
00:12:14,799 --> 00:12:20,320
What if the person you killed
was the imposter?

115
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,399
No way.

116
00:12:21,639 --> 00:12:25,440
I took you for the best strategist
in this mansion.

117
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:28,120
It seems that's not the case.

118
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:32,159
I'll find out what happened.

119
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:37,080
Unless it's urgent,
let's not meet in the next few days.

120
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:51,000
My apologies.

121
00:12:51,679 --> 00:12:53,080
(My brother returned injured.)

122
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:55,320
(Can't I even visit him?)

123
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,240
(Zhaoxi.)

124
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,360
We haven't seen each other

125
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:03,120
(for five years, Zhaoxi.)

126
00:13:03,679 --> 00:13:06,360
(How come you don't speak to me at all?)

127
00:13:08,879 --> 00:13:09,840
(He's not Zhaoxi.)

128
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,240
Zhaoxi is dead.

129
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,480
Why didn't you wear the jade pendant

130
00:13:14,559 --> 00:13:15,759
you have had since childhood?

131
00:13:18,039 --> 00:13:20,240
Let's find out if he's an imposter.

132
00:13:25,519 --> 00:13:26,879
(Why is the Gu family)

133
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:29,639
(treating Gu Zhaoxi this way?)

134
00:13:41,759 --> 00:13:43,000
This is from Master Wenshuang.

135
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:55,360
Yuluo, this is the peach blossom wine
I prepared for you.

136
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:56,679
And I heard

137
00:13:57,039 --> 00:14:00,799
that it tastes even better
after getting stored under a tree

138
00:14:01,279 --> 00:14:02,480
for a while.

139
00:14:04,399 --> 00:14:06,919
What's wrong? Don't you want it?

140
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:08,320
Of course, I do.

141
00:14:08,799 --> 00:14:11,200
Let's drink it when you take it out.

142
00:14:58,919 --> 00:15:01,200
Master Wenshuang,
everyone is looking for you.

143
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:03,639
It's getting late.
You should go back now.

144
00:15:05,279 --> 00:15:06,919
I don't want to be a Master at all.

145
00:15:07,559 --> 00:15:08,879
I prefer it like this,

146
00:15:09,399 --> 00:15:10,559
practicing martial arts

147
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,279
and sparring with you.

148
00:15:13,639 --> 00:15:16,720
I leave the family's affairs to Xuanji

149
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:20,279
and business matters to Chaosheng.

150
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:25,360
And the Xuanji Pavilion
belongs to Zhaoxi's mother.

151
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:29,639
I don't

152
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:32,080
want to bear too many expectations.

153
00:15:33,799 --> 00:15:35,200
I want us to remain like this.

154
00:15:55,279 --> 00:15:56,080
Take it away.

155
00:15:57,039 --> 00:15:58,440
And the lanterns in the yard.

156
00:16:00,039 --> 00:16:00,539
Understood.

157
00:16:02,879 --> 00:16:04,759
What's wrong? Got any updates?

158
00:16:07,039 --> 00:16:09,600
People monitoring
the Right Chancellor's mansion said

159
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:11,720
that they didn't see
who stole the ledger.

160
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:14,559
That person mastered qinggong.

161
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:19,120
I suspect it's the same person
I ran into at the Xuanji Pavilion.

162
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:23,000
But I think this person looks familiar.

163
00:16:25,159 --> 00:16:28,120
Any updates from the others?

164
00:16:28,759 --> 00:16:30,320
That person got away.

165
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:33,080
But those who kept an eye on the palace

166
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:35,480
said that General Shen's faction

167
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:41,879
presented the ledger and key evidence
among those who impeached Princess Shang.

168
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:44,879
General Shen is upright and unyielding.

169
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:48,320
If he's the one involved,

170
00:16:49,519 --> 00:16:52,799
I believe he will clear the names
of the wrongly accused.

171
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:56,960
Shall we keep an eye
on the Right Chancellor?

172
00:16:57,159 --> 00:16:59,240
No need. The matter is settled.

173
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,360
Get our people back.

174
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:03,720
We should stay out of the other matters.

175
00:17:05,079 --> 00:17:05,579
Understood.

176
00:17:38,119 --> 00:17:40,799
If you keep conceding pieces to me,

177
00:17:41,720 --> 00:17:43,599
I'm afraid you won't be able to win.

178
00:17:45,039 --> 00:17:48,799
Didn't you say your husband
has a gentle personality?

179
00:17:49,119 --> 00:17:51,440
Doesn't he make moves this way?

180
00:17:54,960 --> 00:17:56,920
His gentleness is a way
of staying low-key.

181
00:17:57,799 --> 00:18:01,519
Encirclement rather than assault.
His chess play is highly restrained.

182
00:18:02,240 --> 00:18:06,680
But you always retreat
before the assault.

183
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:19,839
I'm a bit tired of it.
Let's play another day.

184
00:18:21,319 --> 00:18:22,559
Did I do something wrong?

185
00:18:24,599 --> 00:18:27,920
I'm sorry my poor chess skills
annoyed you, dear.

186
00:18:29,240 --> 00:18:30,440
You're a great couple.

187
00:18:30,799 --> 00:18:33,759
Master Zhaoxi is still missing,
and you've found a substitute

188
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:36,920
to do everything you've done with him.

189
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:41,200
And I'm just a paid stand-in.

190
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:50,000
I'm nothing but an imposter to you.

191
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:52,880
I feel quite guilty.

192
00:18:53,319 --> 00:18:55,279
It's enviable that Master Zhaoxi

193
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:57,440
has such a soulmate.

194
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:19,640
Any new leads
on Master Zhaoxi's murderer?

195
00:19:25,200 --> 00:19:28,519
There's one thing
I've never done with Zhaoxi.

196
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:30,079
Shall we?

197
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:43,960
Since you invited me,
I shall certainly join you.

198
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:46,319
Let's go then.

199
00:20:33,616 --> 00:20:38,679
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

200
00:20:39,216 --> 00:20:44,537
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

201
00:20:45,104 --> 00:20:51,732
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

202
00:20:51,732 --> 00:20:56,496
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

203
00:20:56,496 --> 00:20:58,832
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

204
00:20:58,832 --> 00:21:05,532
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

205
00:21:05,532 --> 00:21:12,304
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

206
00:21:12,304 --> 00:21:19,440
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

207
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:23,824
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

208
00:21:23,824 --> 00:21:26,448
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

209
00:21:26,448 --> 00:21:33,082
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

210
00:21:33,082 --> 00:21:39,632
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

211
00:21:39,632 --> 00:21:46,756
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

212
00:21:46,846 --> 00:21:51,216
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

213
00:21:51,216 --> 00:21:53,924
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

214
00:21:53,924 --> 00:21:59,824
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

215
